Package: bskyconf
Title: Track and Display Bluesky Conference Posts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sharon", "Machlis", , "sharon@machlis.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fetch, deduplicate, and display Bluesky posts for conference
    hashtags. Includes a Shiny app for browsing posts with date and author
    filtering, metric cards, and CSV export. Designed for automated updates
    via cron and deployment on Shiny Server.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/smach/bskyconf
BugReports: https://github.com/smach/bskyconf/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
